Note: uses older lineage for Delete The 10

Earth + Water = Plant
Earth + Plant = Tree
Tree + Water = River
Earth + River = Delta
River + Tree = Paper
Paper + Plant = Book
Book + Delta = Alphabet
Alphabet + Alphabet = Word
Word + Word = Sentence
Sentence + Wind = Phrase
Book + Phrase = Quote
Alphabet + Quote = Punctuation
Earth + Punctuation = Period
Punctuation + Wind = Comma
Comma + Paper = List
Fire + Period = Stop
List + Quote = Tweet
Stop + Tweet = Delete
Delete + Period = Delete.
Punctuation + Quote = Apostrophe
Book + Period = Full Stop
Book + Full Stop = End
End + Word = The
Apostrophe + The = The’
Delete. + The’ = Delete The
Alphabet + Fire = Alphabet Soup
Apostrophe + Plant = Potato
Alphabet Soup + Potato = Vowel
Delete The + Vowel = Delete The E
Delete The E + Period = Delete The Period
Delete The E + Sentence = Tenet
Delete The E + Tenet = Ten
Delete The Period + Ten = Delete The 10  // 33



Gen 1 - 240 Elements -> 240 Total Elements
Gen 2 - 1796 Elements -> 2036 Total Elements
Gen 3 - 11357 Elements -> 13393 Total Elements

3 - The 20th’s: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + The’ = The 20th
Apostrophe + The 20th = The 20th’s

3 - The 19th: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + The’ = The 20th
Delete The E + The 20th = The 19th

3 - The 30th: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + The’ = The 20th
Delete The 10 + The 20th = The 30th

3 - Potato Punctuation: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Potato = 20 Potatoes
20 Potatoes + Punctuation = Potato Punctuation

3 - 20,000 Potatoes: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Potato = 20 Potatoes
20 Potatoes + Comma = 20,000 Potatoes

3 - 19 Potatoes: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Potato = 20 Potatoes
20 Potatoes + Delete The = 19 Potatoes

3 - Two Thousand Ten: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Delete The Period = 2010
2010 + Phrase = Two Thousand Ten

3 - 2010!: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Delete The Period = 2010
2010 + Punctuation = 2010!

3 - 2010.: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Delete The Period = 2010
2010 + Period = 2010.

3 - 2010,: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Delete The Period = 2010
2010 + Comma = 2010,

3 - 2009: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Delete The Period = 2010
2010 + Delete = 2009

3 - 2010's: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Delete The Period = 2010
2010 + Apostrophe = 2010's

3 - 2010 The: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Delete The Period = 2010
2010 + The’ = 2010 The

3 - 50: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Tenet = 30
20 + 30 = 50

3 - 60: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Tenet = 30
30 + 30 = 60

3 - 30,: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Tenet = 30
30 + Comma = 30,

3 - 29: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Tenet = 30
30 + Delete. = 29

3 - 30’: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Tenet = 30
30 + Apostrophe = 30’

3 - 30.: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Tenet = 30
30 + Full Stop = 30.

3 - 30 Potatoes: 
Delete The 10 + Ten = 20
20 + Tenet = 30
30 + Potato = 30 Potatoes
